  <brief_title>Effect of Liraglutide on the Beta-cell Responsiveness in Subjects With Type 2 Diabetes Compared to a Healthy Control Group</brief_title>
  <official_title>NNC 90-1170 Mechanism of Action: A Double-blind, Randomized, Single-center, Placebo Controlled, Crossover Study to Examine Beta-cell Responsiveness to Graded Glucose Infusion in Subjects With Type 2 Diabetes</official_title>
